rows.label: qev092706_MSG0010
rows.name: Liesel![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0020
rows.name:
When your comms cut out, I thought we'd lost you!
What in the hell happened?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0030
rows.name: Mmm. Indigens decided to give me grief.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0040
rows.name: Give you gr— Whuh?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0045
rows.name: You were attacked?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0050
rows.name:
We got some good data.
Just check the battle log—you'll see.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0060
rows.name: I know I'm somewhat behind schedule...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0070
rows.name:
But at least I'm back on track,
thanks to these BLADEs.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0080
rows.name: Liesel... What am I gonna do with you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0090
rows.name:
I'm sorry... You're the BLADEs who took
up the assignment, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0100
rows.name: I'm grateful. Thank you so, so much.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0110
rows.name: I'm Alicia, an engineer at Grenada.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0120
rows.name: This Skell, Hraesvelg—it's almost entirely her creation.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0130
rows.name:
Liesel and I go way back.
You might even say we're "pals."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0140
rows.name:
The two of us have known each other since back on Earth,
and that's all I am to you, is it? A "pal?"[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0150
rows.name: Oh? Haha! I'm just kidding.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0155
rows.name: "Besties"—is that better?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0160
rows.name: Anyhow...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0170
rows.name:
Hraesvelg's had the green light for mass-production—
all that's left was a few final checks...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0180
rows.name: This'll be a major setback for Grenada...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0190
rows.name: Yeah, about that...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0200
rows.name:
As I see it, operating this Skell demands a higher
level of competence than most others.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0210
rows.name:
For one, the drivetrain feedback is finicky.
And it wasn't half as bad in the bench tests.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0220
rows.name: Huh? I don't understand...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0230
rows.name:
The computer should've modeled it out fine.
Think it's programmed wrong?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0240
rows.name:
If so, that's weird.
Hold on, I'll double-check.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0250
rows.name:
You're right. The values are—
No, this wouldn't account for—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_JNK0260
rows.name: Show Concern

rows.label: qev092706_SEL0270
rows.name: Ask what it was that she found.

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0280
rows.name: This Skell, the Hraesvelg...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0290
rows.name:
There's extra processing going on after it
receives manual input, before hitting the drive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0300
rows.name:
The idea was to filter out unintended
nudges on the controls.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0310
rows.name:
If that process were to bug out,
it'd impede the Skell's movement.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_JNK0320
rows.name: Assist

rows.label: qev092706_SEL0330
rows.name: Offer to lend a hand.

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0340
rows.name:
Thanks. We appreciate the offer, but...
it's not necessary.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0350
rows.name: Alicia isn't the chief engineer for nothing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0360
rows.name: I found our culprit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0365
rows.name: Our proprietary system's control module was fritzing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0370
rows.name:
I've made sure that it won't do so again.
Problem solved.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0380
rows.name: Finally. We're finished, after all these years.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0390
rows.name: Indeed. Now...we just wait for the press release.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0400
rows.name:
All right! Now that that's all squared away,
it's about time we started on the proprietary—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0410
rows.name:
Y-yes...? Ah— Yes, sir.
Of course. Right away.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0420
rows.name: That the boss?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0430
rows.name: The one and only. He wants to see us ASAP.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0440
rows.name:
Not again... If he's got complaints,
he should come over here...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0450
rows.name: He also...asked for you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0460
rows.name: Oh boy. No rest for the wicked...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0470
rows.name: It'll be on me, for hiring BLADE without his say-so.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0480
rows.name: No... I'm the one who went incommunicado in this case.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0490
rows.name: Sorry. It shouldn't take too long.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092706_MSG0495
rows.name: Me and Alicia, we can do all the talking.[ST:wait ]
